tiralabra.datastructure

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • tiralabra.datastructure.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Node>

    public class Node
extends Object
implements Comparable<Node>
    Represents the node in a binary tree. The node includes the character and its count.
